ifier":"OT1236","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/bpdts-ltd","base_path":"/government/organisations/bpdts-ltd","content_id":"fb773252-0759-4339-b3c6-c66a6a46722d","document_type":"organisation","locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"BPDTS Ltd","withdrawn":false,"details":{"logo":{"formatted_title":"BPDTS Ltd","crest":"single-identity"},"brand":"department-for-work-pensions","default_news_image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/default_news_organisation_image_data/file/238/s300_bpdts-logo-960.gif","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/default_news_organisation_image_data/file/238/s960_bpdts-logo-960.gif"}},"links":{},"api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/bpdts-ltd","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/bpdts-ltd"}],"available_translations":[{"title":"We’ve signed the Tech Talent Charter","public_updated_at":"2019-09-26T14:40:14Z","document_type":"news_story","schema_name":"news_article","base_path":"/government/news/we-ve-signed-the-tech-talent-charter","api_path":"/api/content/government/news/we-ve-signed-the-tech-talent-charter","withdrawn":false,"content_id":"060c6820-2012-4d4c-993a-3192b9833dec","locale":"en","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/news/we-ve-signed-the-tech-talent-charter","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/we-ve-signed-the-tech-talent-charter","links":{}}]},"description":"Amy Cross, Agile Delivery Manager and member of our Diversity and Inclusion Steering Group, on why we’ve signed up to the Tech Talent Charter here at BPDTS.","details":{"body":"\u003cp\u003eThis week (23 to 29 September 2019) we’re celebrating National Inclusion Week. As part of these celebrations, we’re really excited to announce that BPDTS Ltd has joined the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.techtalentcharter.co.uk/\"\u003eTech Talent Charter (\u003cabbr title=\"Tech Talent Charter\"\u003eTTC\u003c/abbr\u003e)\u003c/a\u003e. This is a commitment by organisations to a set of undertakings that aim to deliver greater inclusion and diversity in the tech workforce of the UK. Signatories of the charter make a number of pledges in relation to their approach to recruitment and retention.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAlthough it’s very much an employer-led initiative, the \u003cabbr title=\"Tech Talent Charter\"\u003eTTC\u003c/abbr\u003e is supported by the UK Government’s Digital Strategy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn joining the \u003cabbr title=\"Tech Talent Charter\"\u003eTTC\u003c/abbr\u003e, we at BPDTS are proud to stand alongside influential organisations such as the BBC, Lloyds Banking Group, Vodafone and also our civil service colleagues in the Department for Work and Pensions (\u003cabbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\"\u003eDWP\u003c/abbr\u003e) and \u003cabbr title=\"Department for Work and Pensions\"\u003eDWP\u003c/abbr\u003e Digital. We’ll have the opportunity to collaborate with other tech companies to help us support attraction and recruitment, our inclusive initiatives and we’ve also committed to anonymously submit our diversity data for publication.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe’re standing up and shouting about our commitment to creating a fully inclusive and diverse organisation. Our employees have committed to sign our pledge:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eI will treat all my colleagues as equals, respecting, acknowledging and valuing who they are as an individual\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eI will create a space and a culture where we can all be ourselves, free from discrimination or unfair treatment\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eI will stand by all of my colleagues as an ally\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAnd in return we’re signing a collective pledge in \u003cabbr title=\"Tech Talent Charter\"\u003eTTC\u003c/abbr\u003e as part of our commitment to delivery.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Tech Talent Charter\"\u003eTTC\u003c/abbr\u003e give us the platform to not only learn more about how we can develop as an organisation, it gives us a forum to collaborate with other pioneers and leaders on diversity and inclusion, and make our ultimate to commitment to being totally inclusive visible.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe’re serious about inclusivity at BPDTS and we’re not afraid to shout about it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n","image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5d8ccb64e5274a2fb1019bd1/amy-woods-ttc.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5d8ccb6240f0b65e5dbe04b5/amy-woods-ttc.jpg","alt_text":"Amy Woods, Agile Delivery Manager at BPDTS","caption":"","credit":""},"change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2019-09-26T14:29:56.461Z"}]}}